### 2. Insecure Headers
The application doesn't set security-related HTTP headers, making it vulnerable to common web attacks.

**Recommendation**: Use the Helmet middleware to set security headers.

```javascript
// Install helmet: npm install helmet
const helmet = require('helmet');

// Add this middleware after creating the app
app.use(helmet());
